This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and specifically, removing rain from images. The use of a deep neural network also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves data distillation, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the paper's focus on image processing and deep learning could also make it relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
